  m_text: 'Beware! There''s a pit in this level!

    But not that many spikes.


    Keep
    an eye on your fuel, and be careful not to fall! There are no checkpoints, so
    the only way back up is to do it all over again.


    your progress doesn''t
    save on this one either, so you can''t continue when you ragequit.


    This
    would be a good one to start with.'
